    "You've been logging cramps": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You've been logging cramps"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du hast Krämpfe erfasst"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Has registrado cólicos"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous avez noté des crampes"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge title: comfort nudge for cramps"
    },
    "Your average cycle is around %lld days. Cycles shorter than 21 days are worth mentioning to a doctor — it’s a common and treatable pattern.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your average cycle is around %lld days. Cycles shorter than 21 days are worth mentioning to a doctor — it’s a common and treatable pattern."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dein durchschnittlicher Zyklus beträgt etwa %lld Tage. Zyklen unter 21 Tagen solltest du mit einer Ärztin besprechen — das ist ein häufiges und behandelbares Muster."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tu ciclo promedio es de %lld días. Los ciclos de menos de 21 días vale la pena mencionárselos a un médico — es un patrón común y tratable."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Votre cycle moyen dure environ %lld jours. Les cycles inférieurs à 21 jours méritent d’être mentionnés à un médecin — c’est un schéma courant et traitable."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: short cycle, %lld = average cycle length in days"
    },
    "Your average cycle is around %lld days. Cycles over 35 days can have a few different causes — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your average cycle is around %lld days. Cycles over 35 days can have a few different causes — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dein durchschnittlicher Zyklus beträgt etwa %lld Tage. Zyklen über 35 Tage können verschiedene Ursachen haben — eine Ärztin kann helfen, das abzuklären."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tu ciclo promedio es de %lld días. Los ciclos de más de 35 días pueden tener varias causas — un médico puede ayudarte a entender qué está pasando."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Votre cycle moyen dure environ %lld jours. Les cycles supérieurs à 35 jours peuvent avoir plusieurs causes — un médecin peut vous aider à comprendre ce qui se passe."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: long cycle, %lld = average cycle length in days"
    },
    "Periods consistently over 7 days are worth mentioning to a doctor. There are several common, treatable causes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Periods consistently over 7 days are worth mentioning to a doctor. There are several common, treatable causes."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Perioden, die durchgehend über 7 Tage dauern, solltest du mit einer Ärztin besprechen. Es gibt mehrere häufige, behandelbare Ursachen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los períodos que duran más de 7 días de forma constante merecen mencionarse a un médico. Hay varias causas comunes y tratables."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Des règles qui durent régulièrement plus de 7 jours méritent d’être signalées à un médecin. Il existe plusieurs causes courantes et traitables."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: long period"
    },
    "A few things that can help: heat on your lower abdomen, ibuprofen taken with food at the first sign (not after), and magnesium-rich foods like dark chocolate and nuts.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A few things that can help: heat on your lower abdomen, ibuprofen taken with food at the first sign (not after), and magnesium-rich foods like dark chocolate and nuts."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein paar Dinge, die helfen können: Wärme auf dem Unterbauch, Ibuprofen beim ersten Anzeichen mit Essen nehmen (nicht danach) und magnesiumreiche Lebensmittel wie dunkle Schokolade und Nüsse."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Algunas cosas que pueden ayudar: calor en el abdomen inferior, ibuprofeno tomado con comida al primer signo (no después) y alimentos ricos en magnesio como el chocolate negro y los frutos secos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Quelques choses qui peuvent aider : de la chaleur sur le bas-ventre, de l’ibuprofène pris avec de la nourriture aux premiers signes (pas après), et des aliments riches en magnésium comme le chocolat noir et les noix."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: cramps comfort suggestion"
    },
    "Your cramp days are increasing": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your cramp days are increasing"
          }
        },
