      "comment": "Signal title: severe symptom cluster"
    },
    "Period pain that gets worse cycle over cycle is worth mentioning to a doctor. It can have treatable causes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Period pain that gets worse cycle over cycle is worth mentioning to a doctor. It can have treatable causes."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regelschmerzen, die von Zyklus zu Zyklus schlimmer werden, solltest du mit einer Ärztin besprechen. Es kann behandelbare Ursachen geben."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El dolor menstrual que empeora de ciclo en ciclo vale la pena mencionárselo a un médico. Puede tener causas tratables."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Des douleurs menstruelles qui s’aggravent d’un cycle à l’autre méritent d’être signalées à un médecin. Elles peuvent avoir des causes traitables."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body: escalating cramps"
    },
    "Consistently heavy periods are common but worth discussing with a doctor — especially if you’re soaking through protection quickly or feeling fatigued.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Consistently heavy periods are common but worth discussing with a doctor — especially if you’re soaking through protection quickly or feeling fatigued."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Durchgehend starke Perioden sind häufig, aber es lohnt sich, sie mit einer Ärztin zu besprechen — besonders wenn du Schutz schnell durchtränkst oder dich ungewöhnlich müde fühlst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los períodos abundantes de forma constante son comunes, pero vale la pena discutirlos con un médico — especialmente si empapas la protección rápidamente o te sientes inusualmente fatigada."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Des règles constamment abondantes sont courantes mais méritent d’être discutées avec un médecin — surtout si vous saturez rapidement votre protection ou ressentez une fatigue inhabituelles."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body: heavy flow"
    },
    "You often log cramps during your follicular phase, not just your period. This is less typical and worth tracking — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You often log cramps during your follicular phase, not just your period. This is less typical and worth tracking — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du erfasst häufig Krämpfe in deiner Follikelphase, nicht nur während der Periode. Das ist weniger typisch und es lohnt sich, es zu beobachten — eine Ärztin kann helfen herauszufinden, was los ist."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Frecuentemente registras cólicos durante tu fase folicular, no solo durante tu período. Esto es menos típico y vale la pena seguirlo — un médico puede ayudar a entender qué está pasando."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous notez souvent des crampes pendant votre phase folliculaire, pas seulement pendant vos règles. C’est moins courant et cela vaut la peine d’être suivi — un médecin peut vous aider à comprendre ce qui se passe."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body: cramps in follicular phase"
    },
    "You are consistently logging multiple high-intensity symptoms. This pattern is worth discussing with a doctor — there are well-understood and treatable causes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You are consistently logging multiple high-intensity symptoms. This pattern is worth discussing with a doctor — there are well-understood and treatable causes."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du erfasst regelmäßig mehrere starke Symptome. Dieses Muster ist es wert, mit einer Ärztin besprochen zu werden — es gibt gut verstandene und behandelbare Ursachen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Estás registrando de forma constante múltiples síntomas de alta intensidad. Este patrón vale la pena discutirlo con un médico — hay causas bien conocidas y tratables."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous enregistrez régulièrement plusieurs symptômes intenses. Ce schéma mérite d’être discuté avec un médecin — il existe des causes bien comprises et traitables."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body: severe symptom cluster"
    },
    "Cycles shorter than 21 days are worth mentioning to a doctor — it’s a common and treatable pattern.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cycles shorter than 21 days are worth mentioning to a doctor — it’s a common and treatable pattern."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zyklen unter 21 Tagen solltest du mit einer Ärztin besprechen — das ist ein häufiges und behandelbares Muster."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los ciclos de menos de 21 días vale la pena mencionárselos a un médico — es un patrón común y tratable."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les cycles inférieurs à 21 jours méritent d’être mentionnés à un médecin — c’est un schéma courant et traitable."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: short cycle"
    },
    "Cycles over 35 days can have a few different causes — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cycles over 35 days can have a few different causes — a doctor can help figure out what’s going on."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zyklen über 35 Tage können verschiedene Ursachen haben — eine Ärztin kann helfen, das abzuklären."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los ciclos de más de 35 días pueden tener varias causas — un médico puede ayudarte a entender qué está pasando."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les cycles supérieurs à 35 jours peuvent avoir plusieurs causes — un médecin peut vous aider à comprendre ce qui se passe."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: long cycle"
    },
    "Your cycles vary by more than a week from month to month. This is fairly common but worth a chat with a doctor if it's been going on a while.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Your cycles vary by more than a week from month to month. This is fairly common but worth a chat with a doctor if it's been going on a while."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deine Zyklen schwanken von Monat zu Monat um mehr als eine Woche. Das ist recht häufig, aber nach einer Weile lohnt sich ein Gespräch mit einer Ärztin."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tus ciclos varían más de una semana de un mes a otro. Esto es bastante común, pero vale la pena consultarlo con un médico si lleva tiempo ocurriendo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vos cycles varient de plus d’une semaine d’un mois à l’autre. C’est assez courant, mais il est utile d’en parler à un médecin si cela dure depuis un moment."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Nudge body: high variability"
    },
    "Period pain that gets worse cycle over cycle is worth mentioning to a doctor. It can have several treatable causes.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Period pain that gets worse cycle over cycle is worth mentioning to a doctor. It can have several treatable causes."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Regelschmerzen, die von Zyklus zu Zyklus schlimmer werden, solltest du mit einer Ärztin besprechen. Es kann mehrere behandelbare Ursachen geben."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El dolor menstrual que empeora de ciclo en ciclo vale la pena mencionárselo a un médico. Puede tener varias causas tratables."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Des douleurs menstruelles qui s’aggravent d’un cycle à l’autre méritent d’être signalées à un médecin. Elles peuvent avoir plusieurs causes traitables."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body (signals.json): cramps escalating"
    },
    "Consistently heavy periods are worth discussing with a doctor — especially if you are soaking through a pad or tampon within an hour, on multiple consecutive hours, or feeling unusually fatigued.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Consistently heavy periods are worth discussing with a doctor — especially if you are soaking through a pad or tampon within an hour, on multiple consecutive hours, or feeling unusually fatigued."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Durchgehend starke Perioden sind es wert, mit einer Ärztin besprochen zu werden — besonders wenn du Schutz innerhalb einer Stunde durchtränkst, mehrere aufeinanderfolgende Stunden lang, oder dich ungewöhnlich müde fühlst."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los períodos abundantes de forma constante vale la pena discutirlos con un médico — especialmente si empapas una compresa o tampón en una hora, durante varias horas consecutivas, o si te sientes inusualmente fatigada."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Des règles constamment abondantes méritent d’être discutées avec un médecin — surtout si vous saturez une protection en une heure, sur plusieurs heures consécutives, ou si vous vous sentez inhabituellement fatiguée."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body (signals.json): heavy flow"
    },
    "You have been logging heavy flow": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
