    "Cramps outside your period can have several causes. It's worth mentioning to a doctor who can help investigate.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cramps outside your period can have several causes. It's worth mentioning to a doctor who can help investigate."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Krämpfe außerhalb deiner Periode können verschiedene Ursachen haben. Es lohnt sich, das mit einer Ärztin zu besprechen, die helfen kann, die Ursache zu finden."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los cólicos fuera de tu período pueden tener varias causas. Vale la pena mencionárselos a un médico que pueda investigarlos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les crampes en dehors de vos règles peuvent avoir plusieurs causes. Il vaut la peine d’en parler à un médecin qui pourra les investiguer."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body (signals.json): cramps in follicular phase"
    },
    "You've been logging significant mood symptoms in the days before your period across several cycles. If this pattern significantly affects your daily life, your doctor can help — there are recognised approaches that can make a real difference. The IAPMD has specialist support.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You've been logging significant mood symptoms in the days before your period across several cycles. If this pattern significantly affects your daily life, your doctor can help — there are recognised approaches that can make a real difference. The IAPMD has specialist support."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Du hast in mehreren Zyklen erhebliche Stimmungssymptome in den Tagen vor deiner Periode erfasst. Wenn dieses Muster deinen Alltag stark beeinträchtigt, kann deine Ärztin helfen — es gibt anerkannte Ansätze, die wirklich einen Unterschied machen können. Die IAPMD bietet Fachunterstützung."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Has registrado síntomas de ánimo significativos en los días anteriores a tu período durante varios ciclos. Si este patrón afecta significativamente tu vida diaria, tu médico puede ayudar — existen enfoques reconocidos que pueden marcar una gran diferencia. La IAPMD ofrece apoyo especializado."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vous avez noté des symptômes d’humeur significatifs dans les jours précédant vos règles sur plusieurs cycles. Si ce schéma affecte considérablement votre vie quotidienne, votre médecin peut vous aider — il existe des approches reconnues qui peuvent faire une vraie différence. L’IAPMD offre un soutien spécialisé."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Signal body (signals.json): PMDD pattern"
    },
    "Heat can help": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Heat can help"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wärme kann helfen"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
