    "Some people feel mild one-sided pelvic discomfort around ovulation (mittelschmerz). It's common and usually brief.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Some people feel mild one-sided pelvic discomfort around ovulation (mittelschmerz). It's common and usually brief."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Manche Menschen spüren um den Eisprung herum ein leichtes einseitiges Unterleibsziehen (Mittelschmerz). Das ist häufig und meist kurz."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Algunas personas sienten una leve molestia pélvica unilateral alrededor de la ovulación (mittelschmerz). Es común y suele ser breve."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Certaines personnes ressentent une légère gêne pelvienne d'un côté autour de l'ovulation (mittelschmerz). C'est courant et généralement bref."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip body: ovulatory mittelschmerz"
    },
    "Mood may shift": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mood may shift"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Stimmung kann sich verändern"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El estado de ánimo puede cambiar"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "L'humeur peut changer"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip title: luteal"
    },
    "Progesterone rises then drops in the luteal phase. If your mood dips in the second half, that's a recognised pattern.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Progesterone rises then drops in the luteal phase. If your mood dips in the second half, that's a recognised pattern."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Progesteron steigt und fällt dann in der Lutealphase. Wenn deine Stimmung in der zweiten Hälfte sinkt, ist das ein bekanntes Muster."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La progesterona sube y luego baja en la fase lútea. Si tu estado de ánimo decae en la segunda mitad, es un patrón reconocido."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La progestérone monte puis chute pendant la phase lutéale. Si votre humeur baisse dans la seconde moitié, c'est un schéma reconnu."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip body: luteal mood"
    },
    "Magnesium may help": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Magnesium may help"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Magnesium kann helfen"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El magnesio puede ayudar"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le magnésium peut aider"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip title: luteal"
    },
    "Some research links magnesium intake to reduced PMS symptoms. Dark chocolate and nuts are decent sources.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Some research links magnesium intake to reduced PMS symptoms. Dark chocolate and nuts are decent sources."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Einige Studien zeigen, dass Magnesium PMS-Symptome lindern kann. Dunkle Schokolade und Nüsse sind gute Quellen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Algunas investigaciones relacionan el consumo de magnesio con la reducción de los síntomas del SPM. El chocolate negro y los frutos secos son buenas fuentes."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Certaines recherches associent la prise de magnésium à une réduction des symptômes du SPM. Le chocolat noir et les noix en sont de bonnes sources."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip body: luteal magnesium"
    },
    "Sleep changes are normal": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sleep changes are normal"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Schlafveränderungen sind normal"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Los cambios en el sueño son normales"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les changements de sommeil sont normaux"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip title: luteal"
    },
    "Progesterone can affect sleep quality in the luteal phase. Cooler room temperature and consistent sleep times help.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Progesterone can affect sleep quality in the luteal phase. Cooler room temperature and consistent sleep times help."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Progesteron kann die Schlafqualität in der Lutealphase beeinflussen. Eine kühlere Raumtemperatur und regelmäßige Schlafzeiten helfen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La progesterona puede afectar la calidad del sueño en la fase lútea. Una temperatura ambiente más fresca y horarios de sueño regulares ayudan."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La progestérone peut affecter la qualité du sommeil pendant la phase lutéale. Une température ambiante plus fraîche et des horaires de sommeil réguliers aident."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip body: luteal sleep"
    },
    "Reduce salt if bloated": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reduce salt if bloated"
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Salz reduzieren bei Blähungen"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reduce la sal si tienes hinchazón"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Réduire le sel en cas de ballonnements"
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip title: luteal"
    },
    "Bloating is common in the late luteal phase. Reducing salty foods and increasing water can ease it.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bloating is common in the late luteal phase. Reducing salty foods and increasing water can ease it."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Blähungen sind in der späten Lutealphase häufig. Weniger salzige Lebensmittel und mehr Wasser können helfen."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "La hinchazón es común en la fase lútea tardía. Reducir los alimentos salados y aumentar el agua puede aliviarla."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les ballonnements sont courants en fin de phase lutéale. Réduire les aliments salés et augmenter l'apport en eau peut les soulager."
          }
        }
      },
      "comment": "Phase tip body: luteal bloating"
    }
